# User (SystemUser) table/entity reference (Microsoft Dynamics 365)

Person with access to the Microsoft CRM system and who owns objects in the Microsoft CRM database.

> [!NOTE]
> The Microsoft Dynamics 365 User (SystemUser) table extends the [Microsoft Dataverse User (SystemUser) table](/power-apps/developer/data-platform/reference/entities/systemuser).
